{"tid":219644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三劫便利店　斧頭賊落網","createTime":"2017-04-27T10:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T13:25:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc642abda34d7f792e0bc52839aefd790a5b1d5b","tid":219644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20003246&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20003246%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170427&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ace3decc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20003246%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170427&h=46cd8ddd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20003246&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170427</a><br />\n<br />\n三劫便利店　斧頭賊落網<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名持行街紙越南男子，涉於過去8天內持斧頭行劫3便利店，負責調查的新界北總區重案組探員翻看大量天眼錄影片段後，鎖定斧頭賊身份，昨午在屯門將他拘捕，探員在其身上沒撿獲斧頭，不排除他當時正找尋目標再伺機犯案。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n警員將涉嫌持斧劫便利店的疑匪制服。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n越南來港　持行街紙<br />\n<br />\n被捕32歲越南男子姓阮，2006年偷渡來港因犯事被遣返，至2015年再偷渡來港，提出免遣返酷刑聲請獲發行街紙，有刑毀及持假證件案底，報稱無業，居無定所，警方正找尋其犯案用的斧頭。<br />\n3宗劫案首宗於上周二凌晨發生，斧頭賊行劫屯門山景邨商場一便利店，掠8,600元；本周日凌晨，斧頭賊闖長沙灣順寧道一便利店，掠5,800元；前日凌晨，旺角界限街一便利店又遭斧頭賊行劫，失5,800元。新界北總區重案組接手，並將3案合併調查。探員翻看3處案發現場及附近閉路電視錄影片段，昨下午派員在屯門新墟附近埋伏，下午3時目標男子出現，探員將他拘捕。<br />\n■記者：劉柏麟"},{"pid":"9757fa604226a55faec5e72a592c4a2610a4484a","tid":219644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"警員將涉嫌持斧劫便利店的疑匪制服。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170427/large/27la8p03a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F27la8p03a.jpg&h=5dd1e567&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0832abc385afd576e17e713a6229d575ce7a6eb","tid":219644,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"渣古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc041cb1fb5df537dca10f490466a8a4d202fddc","tid":219644,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"2006年偷渡來港因犯事被遣返，至2015年再偷渡來港，提出免遣返酷刑聲請獲發行街紙，有刑毀及持假證件案底<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a681110e9de59bf3d0082ccefe7e2690b555d3","tid":219644,"uid":53403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:30:08.000Z","msg":"斧頭幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb39468864669b0687ede54fd5546d599064535","tid":219644,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"又係越蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fff286bf3073b003a8d97ebf54237804fafc32b","tid":219644,"uid":40409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"斧頭幫大佬係入面訓緊晏覺<br />\n邊個唔怕死嘅行前一步呀"},{"pid":"0702ed5baabae8f11de1d0762a336a4920361865","tid":219644,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-04-27/656/20160427002221.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-04-27%2F656%2F20160427002221.jpg&h=d203cb87&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}